description: A rare opportunity to customize your own single family brownstone in the heart of South Boston. Located one block from coveted Thomas Park sits 2 Pacific St - a stunning 2,400SF single family home spanning over 4 floors. The home is in disrepair, so bring your vision and create a masterpiece you can be proud of! Enter on the parlor level with soaring 10' ceilings featuring 2 impeccably kept marble fireplaces, opportunity to restore periodic detail including custom crown molding and original stair bannisters. Create your dream primary suite floor with room sprawling walk in closet and spa-like bathroom. Floor plan allows for 3 additional bedrooms, office, bonus room leading to your private patio and potential for roof deck with 360 views. Offered at only $375/ft!  Property being sold "as is"
